Goal: 
    - Survive without getting hit as long as possible. 
        - If you get hit by astroid it will reset (you have a total of 3 lives) 
        - Shoot as many astroids to protect yourself 
    

Playing: 
    - Game will immediately start when it is opened. 
    - Tapping WASD will turn you in the corresponding directions, and if you press and hold it will travel in the 
    corresponding direction. 
    - Pressing space bar will shoot the shots 
    - If killed by astroid, you will respawn in the center and loose a life, if you are out of lives the game is over 
    and you can start another round by pressing P
